Tears In the Club
description:
Tears in the Club is a showcase of the latest in cutting edge emotive electronic dance music. The sounds showcased herein represent the culmination of decades of electronic music evolution and innovation. Here, the ultra-futuristic hybrid genres of wave, neogrime, and hypertrance combine to evoke an unmistakeable and unparalleled sonic vision of the future that draws obvious influence from all corners of the electronic music world.

Witness the ethos of trance, trap ,grime and witch house fuse with the pathos of Y2K, 90s R&B and a digitized, cybernetic vision of a future that is far from reality but uncannily close to what can only be described as a shared subconscious vision or expectation of a better future. As the world experiences unparalleled turmoil and uncertainty, a space must exist where the need to dance and the desire to cry can peacefully coexist for a few moments of intensity, emotion, and escape.

CODE001 | LDN: Rapture 4D / Pholo / Gastah / Real Tears / R@ / Eone + More
description:
Introducing CODE: a new forward-thinking club event in London, curated and hosted by two certi-sadboys, Real Tears and Gastah.

Featuring some of the UK's favourite artists from the underground bass scene, CODE is buckling up to deliver a day and night filled with unmissable grime, wave, bassline, trance, wifey and other bass-heavy components.

name: CODE002 | LDN: Vacant / Beau / Rapture 4D / Pholo / Gastah / Real Tears + More
description:
CODE is a new forward-thinking club event in London, curated and hosted by Real Tears and Gastah.

CODE002 will feature some of the UK's favourite artists from the underground bass scene: Vacant, Rapture 4D, Pholo, Gastah, Real Tears, Visene, R@, Beau and Cardio. CODE002 will deliver a night filled with unmissable grime, wave, bassline, trance, nightcore and other bass-heavy components.

Expect euphoric melodies beyond your wildest dreams, techy grime instrumentals that'll supercharge your love for percussion and, overall, an experience packed with emotion.
